      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech_LabAnalyzer项目画一个Git流程图，展示如何把main分支的改动合并到一个尚未开发的特性分支上。标题就叫\"Merge from main onto undeveloped branch\"吧。",
