      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个流程。LR方向可以，这样时间线从左往右比较直观。develop分支先做一个提交，然后切回main再做提交，最后切回develop执行merge main。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "checkout develop",
        "merge main",
        "LR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
