    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来画一下：先放title，然后gitGraph LR，起始一个commit，branch develop后再commit，接着checkout main做commit，最后checkout develop合并main。这样develop就拿到了main的最新改动。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "gitGraph LR",
        "commit",
