        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，develop分支在merge main之前，是不是应该先有个自己的提交？不然它就是个空分支，不太符合实际开发场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
